Daggers 8 is a classic kung fu film starring Yuan Man Meng as the fiercely acrobatic young man and Wilson Tong as the mysterious killer, with Lily Li showing up in the film.

The story revolves around the young man being forbidden to study kung fu, so he goes off in search of a teacher (or several). Lots of entertaining training sequences, specifically the noodles scenes (long-life noodles versus funeral noodles). Lots of flips and somersaults (reminiscent of Yuen Biao). The dubbing is pretty hilarious.
